title: The Grateful Dead - View from the Vault
description: Full concert footage from Three Rivers Stadium in Pittsburgh, PA on July 8, 1990. Setlist includes: "Touch of Grey", "New Minglewood Blues", "Samson and Delilah", "Estimated Prophet", "Terrapin Station", "Black Peter". Along with a couple of Bob Dylan covers: "Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues" and "Knockin' On Heaven's Door". Bonus footage from Cardinal Stadium in Louisville, KY on July 6, 1990 includes 3 extra tracks.
